WorkItem.Description:
1) In the DragNDropSample, disable the "drop me" text block's drag&drop functions by removing the mouse preview events, like so:

<TextBlock Margin="5" Text="Drop Me In Tree!"/>

2) Select a draggable item in the tree view.  The DragNDropController populates its draggableItems collection with the selected item.

3) Click and drag from the "drop me" text block to an insertion point in the tree.  The tree view item you previously selected will be inserted into the tree.

